# Generate API Clients

Generate typed client code from `shared/api-contracts/openapi.yml`.

## Instructions

1. Validate the OpenAPI spec: `task validate-api`
2. Run generation: `task generate-clients`
3. Verify generated code compiles:
{% if "backend" in platforms %}   - `task backend:build`{% endif %}
{% if "web" in platforms %}   - `task web:build`{% endif %}
{% if "android" in platforms %}   - `task android:build`{% endif %}
{% if "ios" in platforms %}   - `task ios:build` (Mac only){% endif %}

## When to Use

- After modifying `shared/api-contracts/openapi.yml`
- After running `$scaffold-feature` or adding endpoints
- User invokes `$generate-clients`
